%% Diagram: Negative caching of NXDOMAIN/NODATA per RFC 2308
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant R as Resolver
    participant A as Auth

    C->>R: Q: missing.example.com A?
    R->>A: Q: missing.example.com A?
    A-->>R: NXDOMAIN + SOA (MIN=3600)
    Note over R: ncache TTL\n= min(SOA.MIN, SOA TTL)\n= 3600 s
    R-->>C: NXDOMAIN (TTL 3600)
    Note over C,R: Within 3600 s — name later created
    C->>R: Q: missing.example.com A?
    R-->>C: NXDOMAIN from cache
    Note over R: After negative TTL expires
    C->>R: Q: missing.example.com A?
    R->>A: Q: missing.example.com A?
    A-->>R: A 192.0.2.10
    R-->>C: A 192.0.2.10
